SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT INVO_NO,INVO_INVDATE, INVO_INVOICENO,INVO_DUEDATE, INVO_CURRENCY, INVO_AACTUALI, INVO_MARKCODETEXT, INVO_MARKCODETEXTDATE , INVO_MARKCODESPEC, INVO_MARKCODESPECDATE, INVO_AACTUALC, INVO_PAYMENTCODE FROM :1/INVO, :1/IDUN WHERE INVO_DEBC_NO=:2 AND (INVO_AACTUALI>0 and INVO_NO=IDUN_NO and IDUN_DUNNLETTER = ':3' and IDUN_DUNNDATEEFFECTIVE= ':4') ORDER BY INVO_INVOICENO FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SELECT DISTINCT INVO_NO,INVO_INVDATE, INVO_INVOICENO,INVO_DUEDATE, INVO_CURRENCY, INVO_AACTUALI, INVO_MARKCODETEXT,INVO_MARKCODETEXTDATE, INVO_MARKCODESPEC, INVO_MARKCODESPECDATE, INVO_AACTUALC, INVO_PAYMENTCODE FROM :1/INVO, :1/MARK b, :1/MARK c WHERE INVO_DEBC_NO= :2 and INVO_AACTUALI<0 AND (INVO_MARKCODESPEC = 0 or INVO_MARKCODESPEC > 0 and INVO_MARKCODESPEC = b.MARK_CODE and b.MARK_SPECINCLETTERPRINTINV = 'Y') AND (INVO_MARKCODETEXT = 0 or INVO_MARKCODETEXT > 0 and INVO_MARKCODETEXT = c.MARK_CODE and c.MARK_SPECINCLETTERPRINTINV = 'Y') ORDER BY INVO_INVOICENO FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

select INVO_NO,INVO_INVDATE,INVO_INVOICENO,INVO_DUEDATE, INVO_CURRENCY,INVO_AACTUALI,INVO_MARKCODETEXT,INVO_MARKCODETEXTDATE,INVO_MARKCODESPEC,INVO_MARKCODESPECDATE,INVO_AACTUALC,INVO_DUNNINGSTOP, INVO_CODDRAFT, INVO_PAYMENTCODE from :1/INVO where INVO_DEBC_NO=:2 AND INVO_AACTUALI<>0 ORDER BY INVO_INVOICENO
